snippet: The Dutch wild-card entry Igor Sijsling beat the eighth-ranked Jo-Wilfried Tsonga of France in the first round of the ABN AMRO World Tennis Tournament.
lead_paragraph: The Dutch wild-card entry Igor Sijsling beat the eighth-ranked Jo-Wilfried Tsonga of France in the first round of the ABN AMRO World Tennis Tournament.

headline.seo: Igor Sijsling Upsets Jo-Wilfried Tsonga at ABN AMRO Tournament
headline.main: Third-Seeded Tsonga Beaten by Wild Card
